flowchart TD
    A[Do you want child entities to be automatically affected by parent operations?] -->|No| B[Do not use cascade]
    A -->|Yes| C[Which operation should cascade?]

    C --> D["PERSIST (save new child with parent?)"]
    D -->|Yes| E[Add CascadeType.PERSIST]
    D -->|No| F

    F["MERGE (update child with parent?)"]
    F -->|Yes| G[Add CascadeType.MERGE]
    F -->|No| H

    H["REMOVE (delete child with parent?)"]
    H -->|Yes| I[Add CascadeType.REMOVE]
    H -->|No| J

    J["REFRESH (refresh child with parent?)"]
    J -->|Yes| K[Add CascadeType.REFRESH]
    J -->|No| L

    L["DETACH (detach child with parent?)"]
    L -->|Yes| M[Add CascadeType.DETACH]
    L -->|No| N

    N[Need all above?]
    N -->|Yes| O[Add CascadeType.ALL]
    N -->|No| P[Combine only needed cascade types]
